originalText.text:
This is my first time getting a "professional" photoshoot working directly with a photographer. Li was very professional and attentive to details. As a person who can read people very well, I can tell this photographer cares deeply about her client's satisfaction, and goes the extra mile to ensure that the photos come out to perfection, which makes me happy.

I appreciated the extra attention and didn't feel like I was just a number, rather i felt it was very personal, intimate, and customized just for me. I don't think I can ever go to Sears or anywhere else for a photoshoot ever again after my experience.

She's the best! Will definitely do business again.
